        .cell.medium-8.margin-bottom-3
          h3.color-purple.padding-top-1.strong WHAT WE ARE DOING
          p We acknowledge that human capital investment is a primary tool for producing inclusive and tangible growth. The wealth and sustainability of nations lies not just in the education of the populace, but in the ability of the youth to produce and maintain the infrastructures and services that drive economic growth.

          p Lilyford empowers youth through capacity building, skills acquisition and provision of repayable soft loans for small scale enterprise for the youth. We also work with initiatives that engages youths in productive ventures and activities, necessary for development of their communities.

          p We also setup skill acquisition centres within identified communities for youths and provide the necessary framework for providing viable opportunities after they have finished their skill acquisition programme either through attachment in businesses in need of their skills or by helping them setup small scale operations, from where they can grow to become employers of labour.
